`src/app/api/**`, `supabase/**`, types). See `docs/UI-SURFACES.md` "Engine-rework HOLD list".

## 4. Conflict hygiene
- Rebase onto `origin/main` frequently (`git fetch origin && git rebase origin/main`) ÔÇö and again
  before opening a PR, to catch the engine-rework merge when it lands.
- Keep PRs small and per-surface; merge often to minimize drift.
- Commit format `type(surface): description`. Atomic commits.

## 5. Verify before done
- `npm run lint` + typecheck clean.
- Visual check in the browser (or screenshot) for any surface you change.
- Don't say "should work" ÔÇö show it.
